### Cart List [POST]
this will be used whenever the customer wants to add new items in their chart

|Field|mandatory|description|
|-----|---------|-----------|
|id_product|Y|--------|
|quantity|Y|---------|
|id_user|N|-----|
|voucher|N|-----|

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "id_product": 1,
            "quantity" : 20,
            "voucher" : "natal"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    
    + Headers
    
            Location: /cart
    
    + Body
            
            {
                "message":"item added to cart"
            }

+ Response 401 (application/json)
    
    + Headers
    
            Location: /cart
    
    + Body
            
            {
                "error":"please enter the correct id_product"
            }

+ Response 500 (application/json)
    
    + Headers
    
            Location: /cart
    
    + Body
            
            {
                "error":"the quanitity should not be 0"
            }

